title: ICE: found unstable fingerprints on test `ui\associated-type-bounds\traits-assoc-type-macros.rs`

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

body:

Instead, this happened: ``` stdout: ------------------------------------------ ------------------------------------------ stderr: ------------------------------------------ thread 'rustc' panicked at
